OL,5, More teenagers are turning away from   
OL,6, traditional media outlets and getting  
OL,7, their news from social media, new      
OL,8, research from Ofcom has shown.         
OL,10,FThe number of people consuming news    
OL,11,Fcontent on TikTok has increased from   
OL,12,F800,000 in 2020 to 3.9 million in 2022.
OL,14,FFor the first time, Instagram is the   
OL,15,Fmost popular news source among younger 
OL,16,Fpeople - used by 29% of teens in 2022 -
OL,17,Fwith TikTok and YouTube close behind.  
OL,19,FBut print, TV and radio news outlets   
OL,20,Fstill dominate in older age groups.    
